<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>OUR GOD IS MARCHING ON</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa hungna lopitak chuh ka mitin ana mu a,
 Lungnatna Grep kikhawlkhawmna apat chuh a chiltha tai;
 A chemzam kawlphe banga te lauhum leh kin A ladawk,
 Pathien Galhatpa chieh.

[V2]
 Lopi, lopi! Halelujah (3)
 Pathien hat a chieh zel.

[V3]
 2. Sepaih tamtak panmuna galven meiah Amah ka mu'i,
 Nitak daikiek namun damah maicham a dawhkhang sak ui;
 A thutanna dik chuh meivak apat chun ka simthei hi,
 Pathien Galhatpa chieh.

[V4]
 3. Kinungtawl kit ngeilo dinga samin pengkun A mut tai,
 A vaihawmna chutphah maah mitin lunggil khen in a;
 A sapna dawng di'n ka tha, kin in! Ka keng nang kipak in,
 Pathien Galhatpa chieh.

[V5]
 4. Tuisuohgiet kanin Krista lili hawih lakah A hung pieng,
 Nang leh kei ei hihdanglam, lopina A hun pienpih a;
 Mi thiennang a A thih bangin, mi suohchakna din thii tiu,
 Pathien Galhatpa chieh.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>159</hymn_number>
</song>